{"tid":2099364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"權鬥重地 公安部長難有好下場","createTime":"2020-07-08T07:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T07:29:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2de1e8f137844cc56955c8247ddb41c7ba6077b0","tid":2099364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/MW6LYBSU7IFQ5WYCD4C4QXWAIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FMW6LYBSU7IFQ5WYCD4C4QXWAIQ%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=65ffa768\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200708%2FMW6LYBSU7IFQ5WYCD4C4QXWAIQ%2F&h=542374c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200708/MW6LYBSU7IFQ5WYCD4C4QXWAIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n權鬥重地 公安部長難有好下場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1QKT75PSRZhbyLU2Iu5qx0g0vGc=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D7DCUU2OHXQSGCNYTAWA6BUWGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1QKT75PSRZhbyLU2Iu5qx0g0vGc%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD7DCUU2OHXQSGCNYTAWA6BUWGA.jpg&h=fdd7f6ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n習近平上台後孟倒戈，為拿下周永康立功。<br />\n<br />\n【新聞背景】公安部作為中共<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n毛澤東時代的公安部長更無一有好下場。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：習清洗公安系統 孟建柱「病重住院」 重兵把守如囚禁 料成徐才厚第二<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛時代部長無一善終<br />\n<br />\n中共建政後首任公安部長是羅瑞卿，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n1972年病死。文革後謝遭中共「掘墓鞭屍」，開除黨籍撤銷原悼詞，並被認定為「反革命集團主犯」。<br />\n<br />\n第三任部長李震亦是軍中出身，文革時因介入高層權鬥失勢畏罪自殺。第四任部長華國鋒，雖後來官居中共黨主席兼總理，但文革結束後被鄧小平等趕下台，抑鬱而終。之後數任部長雖能善終，但到周永康掌權後又再出事，要在秦城監獄度餘生。孟建柱接任公安部長五年，後獲升政治局委員兼中央政法委書記，但現又傳被立案調查，在當局監視中「重病住院」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者"}]}